{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e3bab0593b","title":"给周世钊的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fc4874f8da","index":0,"year":1956,"month":12,"day":5,"articleId":"e3bab0593b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"91132b21c1","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周世钊，字停元，当时任湖南省教育厅副厅长兼湖南省第一师范学校校长。"},{"id":"51b2f37641","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指周世句1950年9月下旬赴北京参加国庆观礼路过许昌时所作的《过许昌》一诗。全诗如下：“野史闻曹操，秋风过许昌。荒城临矿野，断码卧斜阳。满市烟香溢，连唯豆叶长。人民新世纪，谁识邮中王！"},{"id":"0333f83682","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《水调歌头·长江》一首词，毛泽东写于1956年6月。词中的“逝者如斯乎”，在同年12月16日给黄炎培的信中，更正为“逝者如斯夫”。这首词的题目，1957年《诗刊》1月号发表时改为《水调歌头·游泳》"}],"contents":[{"id":"23d04c55c5","type":"title","text":"给周世钟的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b"},{"id":"91132b21c1","type":"paragraph","text":"停元兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b"},{"id":"51b2f37641","type":"paragraph","text":"两次惠书均已收到，情意拳拳，极为高兴。告知我省察形情，尤为有益。校牌仍未写，因提不起这个心情，但却时常在念，总有一天要交帐的。时常记得秋风过许昌之句，无以为答。今年游长江，填了一首水调歌头，录陈审正","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b"},{"id":"0333f83682","type":"subtitle","text":"水调歌头·长江","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b"},{"id":"b66dcdfea5","type":"paragraph","text":"才饮长沙水，又食武昌鱼。万里长江横渡，极目楚天舒。不管风吹浪打，胜似闲庭信步，今日得宽余。子在川上日：浙者如斯平！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b"},{"id":"848d8d51bd","type":"paragraph","text":"风墙动，龟蛇静，起宏图。一桥飞架南北，天变通途。更立西江石壁，截断巫山云雨，高峡出平湖。神女应无盖，当惊世界殊。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b"},{"id":"f2352e2f5d","type":"paragraph","text":"暂时不会出国，你们的意见是正确的。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b"},{"id":"de3a47e1d9","type":"subtitle","text":"问好！毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b"},{"id":"b6cd1347dc","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年十二月五日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b"}],"page":{"id":"c183de142b","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e3bab0593b","start":164,"end":165}}}},"__N_SSG":true}